body:
Date: {{date}}

To: Assigned Vocational Rehabilitation Counselor (VRC)
VA Regional Office

Subject: Request for Written Rationale and Administrative Records (38 C.F.R. § 21.50)
Veteran: {{userName}}
VA Claim Number: {{claimNumber}}

Dear Counselor,

I am writing to formally request a written rationale and a copy of the complete administrative record/counseling narrative concerning our conversation on {{dateOfConversation}}.

During that discussion, it was indicated that:
"{{whatVrcSaid}}"

Under 38 C.F.R. § 21.50 and M28C procedural requirements, the VA must provide a veteran with a clear, written explanation of any decision affecting their eligibility, entitlement, or rehabilitation plan, including the specific reasons and the evidence relied upon. 

To ensure I have a complete understanding of my status and to support any subsequent reviews or appeal lanes, I request the following records:
{{requestedRecords}}

Please provide these documents at your earliest convenience. Thank you for your assistance.

Sincerely,

{{userName}}
